title: The Dead Secret
creator: Wilkie Collins
description: LibriVox recording of The Dead Secret, by Wilkie Collins. "Everything in life has a price. May be, telling a Secret has the highest. However, not telling may be worse. What will Sarah choose? will she tell the Secret which destroyed her life?" (Summary by Stav Nisser) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. Download M4B Part 1 (153MB) Download M4B Part 2 (147MB) Download M4B Part 3 (146MB)
